    <bcl:section id="d2e317">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Development potential relief — non-disqualifying exemption</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>5</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The exemption under the Industrial and Business Property Exemption Regulation, B.C. Reg. 485/83, is prescribed for the purposes of section 198.1 (6) (b) (ii) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/03026_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Community Charter</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
